title: #92Noon! Twins/Utecht/Birk/Sterling
description: The Twins/Yankees obsession again starts the show after the 14-12 game last night, football & life in the middle hour as former Gophers/Colts/SB winning TE Ben Utecht is in studio. Matt Birk in for most of final hour, and show ends with Yankees radio voice John Sterling on the hotline!
